{"tid":295661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[仲有黨]四川茂縣山泥傾瀉　幾乎整個村組逾百人被掩埋","createTime":"2017-06-24T02:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T20:26:00.000Z","uid":51271,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"046c4be1db1ab0f6f8c61de627afdd95d4c4554c","tid":295661,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T02:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1338021_1_20170624102716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1338021_1_20170624102716.jpg&h=4177dc2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四川茂縣的暴雨引發山泥傾瀉，疊溪鎮新磨村40多戶過百人被掩埋，堵塞2公里河道，據茂縣宣傳部表示，準確地點為新磨村新村組，幾乎整個村組被掩埋。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地清晨6時，從片段所見，大片山泥及大型石塊將很多房屋掩埋，當局暫時未能估計山泥傾瀉面積。救援人員已經趕赴現場參與搜救，又出動多部鏟泥車協助拯救及清理。茂縣縣委、縣政府緊急啟動一級特大型地質災害險情和災情應急響應。國土資源部已經啓動地質災害三級應急回應，專家組正在前往現場。<br />\n<br />\n當局從阿壩消防正調配汶川、理縣、馬爾康的救援力量到場拯救。"},{"pid":"730fdd4b802bb3ce5e9b7448a7156d618d75bc26","tid":295661,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T02:56:04.000Z","msg":"正評不解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090aa6a7df8f4071955d1675a73c02172083c959","tid":295661,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T02:56:56.000Z","msg":"恐怖<br />\n希望佢地下世不做中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c26b4308083dc6b206e800eaca3e4272de9a92","tid":295661,"uid":31447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T02:57:34.000Z","msg":"🎉🎉🎉🎉🎉🎉🎉🎉🎉🎉"},{"pid":"58ddb22f00ada8cf75bdfda43b51b1ad89c5e0fb","tid":295661,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T02:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50ed6bbc27a9f27332784858c1173181f4ba25d","tid":295661,"uid":72827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T02:57